    |
2)Pull the Icicles in this order:- 2, 3, 1, 4 and the door will now open.
3)Once inside the palace pick up the brush.Pick up the dice on the table and
throw them. Each time you throw the dice different doors will open in the
corridor. The diagram below will help you complete this part of the game.

