FIVE WAYS TO WIN:
1 Find all eight explosives and the timed detonator. Go to Damocles. Drop
  seven explosives and set the eighth to detonate. Depart posthaste and
  collect reward: $10,000,000. Note that you can bargain the State
  President up to $25,000,000 by turning down her first offers.
